y a matter of time before they come out to the streets. So that makes sense."), mdx("p", null, "But what changed between me from three years ago and me today? It hasn\u2019t been truly a drastic change in perspective, but it\u2019s a notable one. As of today, I still don\u2019t have any Black friends. "), mdx("p", null, "I guess some possible reasons are:"), mdx("ul", null, mdx("li", {
